| 主題 | 参照 |
|---|---|
| コードベース調査・CA 洗い出し | [`clean-architecture-violation-fix-workflow/SKILL.md`](../skills/clean-architecture-violation-fix-workflow/SKILL.md) セクション0 |
| 本番の断定 | [`gcp-available.mdc`](gcp-available.mdc)、[`agent-operational-canonical.md`](../skills/clean-architecture-violation-fix-workflow/references/agent-operational-canonical.md) |
